{"type": "article", "id": 23382, "title": "nendo 三角板手表", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-07T07:00:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606160154YLIlUEVsae6Qj9A2.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是 Nendo 为致敬绘图人员系列手表推出的新款，之前两款 01 Scale 和 02 Stencil 的分别取材于直尺和手绘工具尺，表盘内的刻度与尺子的刻度相对应。而这一款则取材于三角板，表盘内有三角板上的方形网格，另有数字刻度和两圈秒表刻度，是刻度最明确的一款手表。表盘直径 36 毫米，用不锈钢制作，有棕色、海军蓝和灰色三种，都配有相应颜色的皮质表带。售价 145.83 英镑，<a href=\"https://www.dezeenwatchstore.com/shop/all/draftsman-03-grid/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160152YzJH4ni2fNuKb635.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160152nvRaz9LjNrf7mcVE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.83012821\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160152ZUOy20pkSDJxFrKe.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66773504\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160153EHjUnkdwF38qM5zX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160153XExzCkIucOYJQSv0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}